{"tid":1452830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1PM 1PM 1PM大家同我入機場","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:38:56.000Z","uid":271353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06e36285b797f22fd791bed24c828a174085f69e","tid":1452830,"uid":271353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=905d4333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=4b66ae7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"03c563444d8ebc96998e021df6fd32ded0e2b32f","tid":1452830,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}